relationship: BFO:0000055 OHD:0000052 ! dental healthcare provider role
relationship: OBI:0000299 OHD:0000010 ! dental finding
property_value: IAO:0000116 "Melissa Haendel 4/12/2012: There can be more than one dental exam that occurs during a dental visit." xsd:string
