id: OHD:0000170
name: dental therapist role
def: "a dentist role that inheres in a person a dentist who practices as part of the dental team to provide educational, clinical and therapeutic patient services; and can provide basic preventive and restorative treatment to children and adults, and extractions of primary (baby) teeth under the supervision of a dentist" []
