[Term]
id: OHD:0000189
name: restored tooth
def: "A tooth that has been restored by using dental restoration material to replace decayed or missing parts of the tooth." []
is_a: UBERON:0001091
intersection_of: UBERON:0001091
intersection_of: BFO:0000051 OHD:0000000 ! dental restoration material
