[Term]
id: OHD:0001026
name: resin-modified glass ionomer dental restoration material
def: "An acid-base cement dental restoration material with modification of  glass ionomer cement with some monomer component and associated activator initiator system to facilitate light and chemically activated polymerization reaction." []
comment: The monomer is typically 2-hydroxyethyl methacrylate, HEMA, and the initiator is camphorquinone. Resin-modified glass-ionomers set by the twin processes of neutralization (acid-base reaction) and addition polymerization, and the resulting material has a complicated structure based on the combined products of these two reactions.
is_a: OHD:0001021 ! acid-base cement dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-08-08T12:27:23Z" xsd:dateTime
property_value: IAO:0000119 "doi: 10.3390/jfb7030016" xsd:string

[Term]
id: OHD:0001032
name: glass matrix ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A ceramic dental restoration material that contains crystallized ceramic portions which are uniformally distributed within a glass phase." [] {IAO:0000119="https://doi.org/10.3390/ma16247541"}
is_a: OHD:0000135 ! ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:39:47Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001033
name: polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A ceramic dental restoration material that contains small crystals, also known as grains, that are separated by grain boundaries and present a random crystallographic orientation , that do not contain a glass phase." []
is_a: OHD:0000135 ! ceramic dental restoration material
relationship: BFO:0000051 OHD:0001079 ! zirconium oxide
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:41:52Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001034
name: zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material that contains Zirconia which is partially stabilized zirconium oxide usually in the tetragonal phase." [] {IAO:0000119="ISBN: 9780323697552"}
is_a: OHD:0001033 ! polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
relationship: BFO:0000051 OHD:0001080 ! yttrium oxide
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:42:45Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001035
name: 3Y-TZP zirconia ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material that contains the first generation of dental zirconia fully stabilized with yttria (Y2O3) which are chiefly composed of the tetragonal phase (tetragonal zirconia polycrystals : TZPs) and are stabilized at room temperature with the addition of 3 mol% of yttrium oxide (3Y-TZP)." []
is_a: OHD:0001034 ! zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:43:04Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001036
name: 4Y-PSZ zirconia ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material that contains the next generation of dental zirconia with the addition of transparent, non-birefringent, cubic-phase stabilized with higher yttrium oxide (of approximately 25% of the cubic phase achieved with 4 mol% of yttrium oxide) with increased translucency in relation to 3Y-TZP for monolithic applications." []
is_a: OHD:0001034 ! zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:43:16Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001037
name: 5Y-PSZ zirconia ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material that contains zirconia with increased yttrium oxide (5-8% mol)" []
is_a: OHD:0001034 ! zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:43:35Z" xsd:dateTime
property_value: IAO:0000118 "ultra translucent zironia" xsd:string

[Term]
id: OHD:0001038
name: multichromatic zirconia ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material that contains additions of layers of different pigments to provide a graded shade between the cervical and the incisal portion of the restoration to mimic the natural tooth appearance." []
is_a: OHD:0001034 ! zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:43:50Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001039
name: multilayered zirconia ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material that contains layered structure composed of different compositions of dental zirconias to provide graded structures that mimic not only the shade, but the translucency and esthetic appearance of natural teeth." []
is_a: OHD:0001034 ! zirconia polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:44:12Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001040
name: polycrystalline composite ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material that combines different cryatalline phases to improve specific properties." [] {IAO:0000119="doi: 10.3390/ma16247541"}
is_a: OHD:0001033 ! polycrystalline ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:44:39Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001041
name: zirconia toughened alumina ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A polycrystalline composite ceramic dental restoration material that combines zirconium to increase the material's mechanical and esthetic properties." []
is_a: OHD:0001040 ! polycrystalline composite ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:44:55Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001042
name: zinc phosphate cement dental restoration material
def: "An acid-base cement dental restoration material containing zinc-oxide and magnesium oxide as a powder component with phosphoric acid as liquid component to complete the acid-base reaction." []
is_a: OHD:0001021 ! acid-base cement dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-09-14T16:34:50Z" xsd:dateTime
