[Term]
id: OHD:0001043
name: zinc polycarboxylate cement dental restoration material
def: "An acid-base cement dental restoration material containing zinc-oxide and magnesium oxide as a powder component with polyacrylic acid and water as liquid component to complete the acid-base reaction." []
