[Term]
id: OHD:0010242
name: temporomandibular joint pain attributed to disc displacement without reduction
def: "Secondary temporomandibulare join pain due to TMJ disc displacement without reduction, which has been diagnosed by jaw locking or limitation of jaw opening. Along with evidence of pain developing in close temporal relation to the disc dsiplacement, a significant worsening in pain paralelle." []
