[Term]
id: OHD:0010250
name: idiopathic trigeminal neuralgia with concomitant continuous pain
def: "Idiopathic trigeminal neuralgia with recurrent paroxysms of unilateral facial pain that is concomitant continuous of near-continuous pain between attacks in the affected trigeminal distirbution." []
