[Term]
id: OHD:0010256
name: orofacial migraine
def: "Episodic or chronic pain exclusively in the orofacial region, without head pain, with the characteristics and associated features of 1. Migraine described in ICHD-3." []
comment: ICOP number: 5.1
subset: OHD:0010296
is_a: OHD:0010255 ! orofacial pain with headache presentation
